         <head>Canto de Trilla</head>
         <p xml:lang="arn"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="amun" pos="V" corresp="go/walk"><m baseForm="amu" type="root" corresp="go/walk">Ámo</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">lé</m><m baseForm="iyu" type="ind1d">yo</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="amun" pos="V" corresp="go/walk"><m baseForm="amu" type="root" corresp="go/walk">ámo</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">lé</m><m baseForm="iyu" type="ind1d">yu</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">cháchan</m></w>. <lb/> ¿<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chem" pos="WH" corresp="why/what"><m baseForm="chem" type="particle" corresp="why/what">Chém</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="anta" pos="IP" corresp="?" ana="See Smeets 2008, 32.9"><m baseForm="anta" type="root" corresp="?">anta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="püñon" pos="V" corresp="step on/stomp"><m baseForm="püño" type="root" corresp="step on/stomp">pəño</m>-<m baseForm="pe" type="px">pe</m><m baseForm="fi" type="3dir">v</m><m baseForm="imi" type="ind2s">ími</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">cháchan</m></w>? <lb/> ¿<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kawella" pos="N" corresp="barley"><m baseForm="kawella" type="root" corresp="barley">Kaweʎa</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="anta" pos="IP" corresp="?" ana="See Smeets 2008, 32.9"><m baseForm="anta" type="root" corresp="?">anchi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="püñon" pos="V" corresp="step on/stomp"><m baseForm="püño" type="root" corresp="step on/stomp">pəño</m>-<m baseForm="pe" type="px">pe</m><m baseForm="fi" type="3dir">v</m><m baseForm="imi" type="ind2s">ími</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>? <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="famün" pos="V" corresp="be thus"><m baseForm="fam" type="root" corresp="thus">Fam</m><m baseForm="ka" type="cont">ka</m><m baseForm="ke" type="habit">ke</m><m baseForm="fu" type="bi">fu</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="ind1s">n</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tañi" pos="PP" corresp="my"><m baseForm="tañi" type="1s" corresp="my">tañi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="püñon" pos="V" corresp="step on/stomp"><m baseForm="püño" type="root" corresp="step on/stomp">pəño</m><m baseForm="yüm" type="temp">yəm</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tañi" pos="PP" corresp="my"><m baseForm="tañi" type="1s" corresp="my">tañi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kawella" pos="N" corresp="barley"><m baseForm="kawella" type="root" corresp="barley">kaweʎá</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chacha</m></w> yem.<lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="trekan" pos="V" corresp="walk/step"><m baseForm="treka" type="root" corresp="walk/step">T’eka</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">le</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋe</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="amun" pos="V" corresp="go/walk"><m baseForm="amu" type="root" corresp="go/walk">amo</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">le</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋe</m></w>; <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tüfeychi" pos="DP" corresp="that"><m baseForm="tüfeychi" type="DP">Təvei</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tüfeychi" pos="DP" corresp="that"><m baseForm="tüfeychi" type="DP">təvei</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>. <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tüfeychi" pos="DP" corresp="that"><m baseForm="tüfeychi" type="DP">Təvei</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tüfeychi" pos="DP" corresp="that"><m baseForm="tüfeychi" type="DP">təvei</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="amun" pos="V" corresp="go/walk"><m baseForm="amu" type="root" corresp="go/walk">amu</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">le</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋe</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>. <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tiken" pos="V" corresp="touch?"><m baseForm="tike" type="root" corresp="touch?">Tike</m><m baseForm="elmew" type="ind3-2">qelmu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="müta" pos="N" corresp="horn"><m baseForm="müta" type="root" corresp="horn">məta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="waka" pos="N" corresp="cow" source="sp:vaca"><m baseForm="waka" type="root" corresp="cow">waka</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="tüfa" pos="DP"><m baseForm="tüfa" type="DP">təv’e</m></w> <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="repülen" pos="V" corresp="copulate"><m baseForm="repü" type="root" corresp="fire drill/copulation">Repə</m><m baseForm="le" type="vb">le</m><m baseForm="ke" type="habit">ke</m><m baseForm="elmew" type="ind3-2">qelmu</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>. <lb/> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="amun" pos="V" corresp="go/walk"><m baseForm="amu" type="root" corresp="go/walk">Amu</m><m baseForm="(kü)le" type="prog">le</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋe</m></w>.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Amuleyu, chachan; amuleyu, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chachan" pos="N" corresp="friend"><m baseForm="chachan" type="root" corresp="friend">chachan</m></w>. Təv’e, təv’e pəñokilmi, doʎem lakarkilmi D’oʎem-meu, təvechi d’oʎem-meu . </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">"ʎawetuav’in təveichi pətapra”</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">“nəkafíŋe kut’i-meu, ʎawetoafími”</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">¿Chumlei?, ¿nielai kiñentəkual, kavo? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">¿Nielayam pulku kiñentəkual? <lb/> V’enten as’t’üi tañi mapu, venten kədautúi. Pulku piŋepen. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Məlei ka. ¿Chumlei, at’ei tañi təkun? </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Pəchin faltai ta təv’e; deuma at’ekai ta təve.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Təv’a mai, kavú; ʎaufiŋe tami mapu.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Deui mai tami kədau, tañi kav’u kənofiyem; at’e tami təkun.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Kəme mai tañi v’ərenefiel; kəmì mai tañi kədau-mu vrenefiel. Deui mai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> kədau; məlì mai pülku; putual mai tami mapu ʎa qav’imi mai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Avle mai, afalé “afí” piaqen. Feimu venten mai pulku pipiekanu tañi pu kona (tañi mapu) təv’ai eŋn. Av’le mai “afí” piaqen. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Femi mai, putuai eŋn; is’t’oviʎ eloayu mai, eloayu is’t’oviʎ mai, tami putua tami mapuʎa mai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Vei ürkemai; kəme mai <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> e!oviel int’u yewenaqelmai afelnoatoam <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> pu kona. Afui mai təvachi kədau, feimeu pulku vi pieno təvai eŋn. Kəmì <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> vreneviel mai. </p>

         <p xml:lang="arn">Putoaiñ mai, <lb/> Moŋelmu <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ñi" pos="PP" corresp="his/her/their"><m baseForm="ñi" type="3">ñi</m></w> taiñ piuke <lb/> Putuʎai mai <lb/> Akui taiñ antüi ʎemai, <lb/> Taiñ votoam ka, <lb/> Taiñ vottoam ʎemai,<lb/> Taiñ putu ʎamai .<lb/> N̰olin, anai, pulku-meu. </p>

